gradMethod.ch:
"期初-課程說明與規劃：3小時;
服務學習籌備：3小時;
期中-進度報告與反思：3小時;
服務學習進行：至少3小時;
期末-成果發表、反思與回饋：3小時;
總計共15小時課程認證時數。"

gradMethod.en:
"Course introduction and planning of service learning: 3 hours;
Preparation of service learning: 3 hours;
Midterm presentation--progress of service learning: 3 hours;
Implementation of service learning: at least 3 hours; 
Final presentation and feedback: 3 hours;
Total: 15 hours obtained."
